News.Title: Presstonic Engineering Wins ₹1.15 Billion Mumbai Metro Contract
News.Summary: Presstonic Engineering secures major Mumbai Metro project contract valued at ₹1.15 billion, marking significant milestone for the SME with ₹70 crore market capitalization.

News.Title: Presstonic Engineering Secures 145.1 Million Rupee Order from BEML
News.Summary: Presstonic Engineering has received a purchase order from BEML (formerly Bharat Earth Movers Limited) valued at 145.1 million rupees. This significant order is expected to boost Presstonic Engineering's revenue and potentially strengthen its position in the engineering sector.
